    Product description

    Maximum Accuracy for You and Your Family

    NexTemp single-use thermometers virtually eliminate the risk of spreading illness by providing a clean instrument that is used once and then discarded. And, the unsurpassed accuracy of NexTemp thermometers provides peace of mind, knowing you have the best possible care for you and your loved ones.


    Medical Indicators has been proudly manufacturing NexTemp thermometers in the USA for more than 30 years!


    NexTemp thermometers utilize a remarkable innovation known as NexTemp Liquid Crystal Technology. The heat-sensitive liquid crystals measure and display body temperature, delivering unsurpassed accuracy and reliability. Available in Fahrenheit and Celsius, NexTemp thermometers are accurate to 0.2F/ 0.1 C.


    Medical Indicators is proud to manufacture our American-made thermometers for doctors, hospitals, teaching institutions, government entities, and medical facilities around the world. And now were proud to offer the same level of safety and security for individuals and families, too!
